content:
Known across the galaxy as the most poppin’ intergalactic party of the year, Countdown is blasting off into 2020 with the largest New Year’s Eve party on the West Coast. This year, we’re entering another dimension with an all-new alien theme, four reimagined extraterrestrial stages—the Mothership, the Nebula, Area 51, and Twilight Zone—and some hidden surprises you won’t want to miss.
